SUMMARY (the human-readable version)

You can use this CMS for free — including on commercial sites and on
sites you sell services around — as long as the credit byline in the
footer ("Site built by Cynthia Brown") remains visible and links to
https://cynthia-brown.com.

If you want to remove or alter the byline, contact the author for a
paid license: hi@cynthia-brown.com.


